  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 13th Level, you learn to perform miracles with your ranged weapons. </p><p>On your first turn in combat, if you are not surprised, you can use your attack action to attack creatures that have not acted yet. </p><p>Choose up to 6 creatures that you can see within 90 feet of you. </p><p>Make a ranged weapon attack targeting each creature. </p><p>On a hit, you deal your weapons damage and can apply a Flurry Technique to each attack made this way. </p><p>Once you've used this feature you must complete a rest before you can use it again.</p>",
